When you start &app;, after a couple of windows (Splash screen, Tip of the Day) the main window will
        be displayed. This window is divided into the following sections (see
         for reference):

entry.para:
If no budgets exist yet, just open a new budget. If only one budget exists, create a copy of it;
                    otherwise user selects one to copy. If a copy is made, then the copy is opened
                    in a new tab.
